==English==
==={{acronym}}===
'''WAGs''' (''plural; not used in the singular'')

#{{informal}} Wives and girlfriends.

====Usage notes====
*'''WAGs''' is used by the British media to refer to the partners of the England football team participating in the 2006 [[World Cup]].
*Whether the term will have any currency after the event remains to be seen.